{"tid":2109114,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"你班haters面對現實啦","createTime":"2020-07-15T04:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T05:17:56.000Z","uid":238051,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b155c4f0200c87c036c102c6f5da4fc1198de8fb","tid":2109114,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:06:53.000Z","msg":"現實就係有錢大晒<br />\n現實就係計邊隊捧杯多 邊隊就成功<br />\n現實係唔care過程架<br />\n<br />\n我隊部分球迷仍然未接受到自己隊波個名要加個「金」字<br />\n其實有乜所謂<br />\n有錢咪有錢<br />\n黑哨咪黑哨<br />\n北京電視機講咗咁多年 推翻咗未？<br />\n喺現實世界 <span class=\"x-large\"><strong>結果就係一切</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你班垃圾咪繼續討論道德問題囉<br />\n俾你講贏又點啫<br />\n我地都係會買鳩晒你嗰隊啲球星<br />\n（除非你哋啲球員太撚垃圾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n我就淨係care五年後你地啲隊加埋捧嘅杯多<br />\n定係我隊啲杯多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9fab6a0a6f28e30eb7a91af26baed913ed0e623","tid":2109114,"uid":6070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:09:34.000Z","msg":"有歐聯未？"},{"pid":"d36064a7b130574df4eca9be915f38fa33582d5a","tid":2109114,"uid":238051,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d9fab6a0a6f28e30eb7a91af26baed913ed0e623","tid":2109114,"uid":6070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:09:34.000Z","msg":"有歐聯未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:18:22.000Z","msg":"五年後都冇先講啦<br />\n有啲隊等一個杯都等30年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a02fd8ad889a8fe03cd2d4af759a1e47d58727","tid":2109114,"uid":6070,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d36064a7b130574df4eca9be915f38fa33582d5a","tid":2109114,"uid":238051,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d9fab6a0a6f28e30eb7a91af26baed913ed0e623","tid":2109114,"uid":6070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:09:34.000Z","msg":"有歐聯未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:18:22.000Z","msg":"五年後都冇